Robert P. Jornayvaz III
Executive Compensation
As Executive Chairman of the Board, President, and Chief Executive Officer at INTREPID POTASH INC, Robert P. Jornayvaz III made $861,096 in total compensation.  Of this total $51,923 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $388,000 was received in stock options, $419,000 was awarded as stock and $2,173 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


