Executive Profile
Robert P. Jornayvaz IIICo-founder, Executive Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President, Intrepid Potash, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships59$861,096As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Robert P. Jornayvaz, III, also known as Bob, serves as an Owner and Principal at Intrepid Mining LLC. Mr. Jornayvaz Co-founded Intrepid Potash, Inc. Mr. Jornayvaz has been an Executive Chairman of the Board at Intrepid Potash, Inc. since May 19, 2010 and has been its Chief Executive Officer and President since August 29, 2014.  He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Intrepid Potash, Inc. from November 2007 to May 19, 2010 and served as its President from February ... 2009 to May 19, 2010. He founded Intrepid Production Corporation in 1984 and serves as its President, where he is responsible for the management of the various Intrepid companies. He served as the Manager of Intrepid Mining since January 2000. He has 27 years of experience in the oil and gas industry. He served as the Chairman of Intrepid Potash, Inc. from November 2007 to May 19, 2010 and has been its Director since December 2007. He serves as a Director of The Fertilizer Institute. Mr. Jornayvaz graduated from Phillips Exeter Academy and holds a B.A. degree from the Plan II Honors Program at the University of Texas.Read Full Background




