Insider Activity


Individual




Robert P. Jornayvaz



Mr. Robert P. Jornayvaz, III, is Executive Chairman, President & CEO at Intrepid Potash, Inc. and Owner at Intrepid Production Corp.
Mr. Jornayvaz was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Intrepid Mining LLC and Co-Founder by Intrepid Oil & Gas LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Texas.



